      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776267607335,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Sourses:\n1. errorEmployees from useFetch()\n2. pendingEmployees from useFetch()\n3. filteredEmployeesList from computed():\n    3.1 employees from useFetch()\n    3.2 fullNameFilter c() from query params\n    3.3 departmentFilter c() from query params\n    3.4 emailFilter c() from query params\n    3.5 positionFilter c() from query params\n    3.6 onlyOvertimeFilter c() from qp\n    3.7 employeeSortingValue c() from qp\n    3.8 employeesSortingType c() from qp\n4. deleteEmployeeResponse.message from ref\n5-11. 3.2-3.8\n12. fulllName from ref\n13. department from ref\n14. email from ref\n15. position from ref\n16. isFormValid from computed\n    16.1 formValidationMessage from ref()\n    16.2 isFormTouched from ref()\n17. allEmployees from computed()\n    17.1 filteredEmployeesList \n18. allOvertimeEmployees from c()\n    18.1 filteredEmployeesList \n19. allPlannedHours from c()\n    19.1 filteredEmployeesList \n    19.2 worklogs from useFetch()\n20. allActualHours from c()\n    20.1 filteredEmployeesList\n    20.2 worklogs\n21, 22. recentWatchedEmployees from ref - CO",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Sourses:\n1. errorEmployees from useFetch()\n2. pendingEmployees from useFetch()\n3. filteredEmployeesList from computed():\n    3.1 employees from useFetch()\n    3.2 fullNameFilter c() from query params\n    3.3 departmentFilter c() from query params\n    3.4 emailFilter c() from query params\n    3.5 positionFilter c() from query params\n    3.6 onlyOvertimeFilter c() from qp\n    3.7 employeeSortingValue c() from qp\n    3.8 employeesSortingType c() from qp\n4. deleteEmployeeResponse.message from ref\n5-11. 3.2-3.8\n12. fulllName from ref\n13. department from ref\n14. email from ref\n15. position from ref\n16. isFormValid from computed\n    16.1 formValidationMessage from ref()\n    16.2 isFormTouched from ref()\n17. allEmployees from computed()\n    17.1 filteredEmployeesList \n18. allOvertimeEmployees from c()\n    18.1 filteredEmployeesList \n19. allPlannedHours from c()\n    19.1 filteredEmployeesList \n    19.2 worklogs from useFetch()\n20. allActualHours from c()\n    20.1 filteredEmployeesList\n    20.2 worklogs\n21, 22. recentWatchedEmployees from ref - CO",
